{"nodes": [{"id": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_frontal_rascunhos_readme_md", "label": "README.md", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/frontal/rascunhos/README.md", "source_location": "L1", "content": "---\ntags:\n  - claude\n  - index\n---\n\n# Thinking Space\n\nClaude's scratchpad for reasoning, drafts, and working through problems before committing conclusions to work notes.\n\n## How This Works\n\n- Notes here are **working drafts**, not final output\n- Named with date and context: `YYYY-MM-DD-descriptive-name.md`\n- Once conclusions land in a work note or decision record, thinking notes stay as reference\n- Tracked in git for portability across machines\n\n## When to Use\n\n- Analyzing a complex problem before writing a [[Decision Record]]\n- Drafting content that will be refined into a work note\n- Reasoning through trade-offs or options\n- Capturing intermediate research before synthesizing\n\n## Linking Convention\n\n- Thinking notes link to the work note or decision they feed into via `## Feeds Into`\n- The final note links back to the thinking note for audit trail\n"}, {"id": "rascunhos_readme_thinking_space", "label": "Thinking Space", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/frontal/rascunhos/README.md", "source_location": "L7"}, {"id": "rascunhos_readme_how_this_works", "label": "How This Works", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/frontal/rascunhos/README.md", "source_location": "L11"}, {"id": "rascunhos_readme_when_to_use", "label": "When to Use", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/frontal/rascunhos/README.md", "source_location": "L18"}, {"id": "rascunhos_readme_linking_convention", "label": "Linking Convention", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "cortex/frontal/rascunhos/README.md", "source_location": "L25"}], "edges": [{"source": "home_michel_documentos_projects_hive_mind_cerebro_cortex_frontal_rascunhos_readme_md", "target": "rascunhos_readme_thinking_space", "relation":